name: Tokyo Night Rain
description:
(to-ma-re series)

When it rains in Tokyo at night, the sky turns this particular shade of pinkish-grey. It’s as if the red helicopter signal lights on top of the tall buildings are blending into the wet sky, tinting it with a light pink shade.

‘To-ma-re’ is the Japanese reading of the ‘stop’ sign featured in every illustration in the series.
